@DanielRona1067 I shouldn't tweet til .5, but I'll make an exception here.

I haven't sold a single $EQR.AX stock, it's so undervalued that I would be crazy even thinking about it.

They're almost printing revenues as big as their marketcap at this rate, they could be acquired anytime 2x higher.

